title: Oct 16 Voting Options
body:
The community has suggested diversifying the FISH vault beyond Cool Cats.

Please vote on what you'd like to see the DAO buy next today.

The DAO treasury currently holds approximately 315 ETH. Note that many community members have suggested we do not spend the ETH all at once today; it may be wise to spread out buys to continue generating new interest in Mutants DAO.
